data.description: OPEN HOUSE 2/25 3-5-PM. This lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bath ranch-style home with updated features like Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring throughout and a newer roof has been well maintained. The Open Concept Living space is perfect for entertaining from the kitchen and open to the family room and dining around the corner. The 4th bedroom upstairs could double as a bonus room which adds an extra touch, and the mentioned amenities including a pool, tennis courts, basketball, and playground contribute to its appeal. Minutes away from the Fayette Piedmont hospital and Trilith. Atlanta International Airport is a 28 min drive but offers shopping, grocery, entertainment and schools minutes away centrally located between Peachtree City and Fayetteville.
